Ayur Healthcare, the pioneers of classical Ayurveda in Australia, are a renowned and trusted clinic situated in Parramatta. We offer expert Ayurvedic consultation, Therapeutic massages & Panchakarma Detox cleansing, Recognized as the "Most Popular Holistic Clinic in Australia" for consecutive years 2020, 2021, and 2022, we were also finalists for the Parramatta Local Businesses Award 2021 and the Australian Small Business Champions Award 2022. With a team of highly skilled Ayurvedic Practitioners holding B.A.M.S, M.S, and M.D degrees and boasting over 25 years of experience.
